# Privacy Policy for MemesGenerator

Last updated: February 12, 2026

## Introduction

MemesGenerator ("we", "our", or "us") built this mobile application as a free app for learning and entertainment purposes.

This page informs users about our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information if anyone decides to use our Service.

By using the app, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

---

## Information We Collect

### 1. Personal Information
We do NOT collect personally identifiable information such as:
- Name
- Email address
- Phone number
- Physical address

### 2. Images and Media
The app may request access to:
- Photos
- Media files
- Device storage

This access is used only to:
- Allow users to select images
- Save generated memes to the device

We do NOT upload, store, or share your images on any server.

### 3. Usage Data
We may collect non-personal information such as:
- App crashes
- Device type
- Operating system version

This is used only to improve app performance.

---

## Internet Usage

If the app connects to the internet (for example, to fetch meme templates), no personal user data is transmitted or stored.

---

## Third-Party Services

The app may use third-party services such as:

- Google Play Services
- AdMob (if ads are enabled)
- Firebase (if analytics or crash reporting is enabled)

These services may collect information as described in their own privacy policies.

You can review:
- https://policies.google.com/privacy

---

## Data Storage

All generated memes are stored locally on your device.

We do not maintain servers or databases that store user content.

---

## Children's Privacy

This app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.

If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us and we will take appropriate action.

---

## Security

We value your trust. Since we do not collect personal data, your information remains on your device.

However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

---

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.

Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.

Users are advised to review this page periodically.

---

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:

your-email@example.com

---

## Consent

By using the MemesGenerator app, you consent to this Privacy Policy.
